title: Cetaphil Moisturizing Cream for Dry, Sensitive Skin 20 oz (2 pack, 40oz total)
description: Cetaphil Moisturizing Cream is specially formulated for the treatment of dry skin localized anywhere on the body surface. It should be applied freely to dry skin as necessary or as directed by a physician. Best results are obtained when it is used directly after bathing, wetting the skin or washing hands.
